data.title: Grand Duchess Xenia Alexandrovna of Russia
data.text:
Grand Duchess Xenia Alexandrovna of Russia (1875-1960), was the eldest daughter of Emperor Alexander III of Russia and Princess Dagmar of Denmark, and wife of Grand Duke Alexander Mikhailovich of Russia.
